title: Warning for commuters for underground strikes
text:
Commuters who rely on the London underground are warned of strike action.
It started yesterday evening and is due to last 24 hours so there could be no services at all today.
It comes as talks failed to agree a pay deal about new night tube services.
London Underground services will start running down later today because of a 24 hour strike Credit: PA Wire Last updated Thu 9 Jul 2015 Travel
